---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Wychwood Partners — Execution Discipline for Scaling Companies"
  description="Wychwood Partners helps growth-stage and PE-backed businesses install operating systems, forecasting discipline, and leadership cadence to scale predictably."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white"></div>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-600 shadow-sm">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
            Fractional • Interim • Full-time COO support
          </p>
          <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-6xl">
            Execution discipline for scaling companies.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 md:text-xl">
            Wychwood Partners installs operating systems, forecasting frameworks, and leadership cadence so growth-stage and PE-backed businesses can scale with clarity, accountability, and predictable outcomes.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-slate-800">
              Book a call
            </a>
            <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-50">
              See how we work
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Operating system</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Roles, rhythms, metrics, and accountability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Forecasting discipline</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Visibility, confidence, and decision velocity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Leadership cadence</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Weekly execution rhythm that sticks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section class="border-t">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">What we install</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
              Clear operating mechanics that turn strategy into execution—without adding bureaucracy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/services" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 hover:underline">View services</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <a href="/services/operational-systems" class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Operational systems</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Operating model, metrics, roles, decision rights, and execution routines.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 group-hover:underline">Learn more →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/services/forecasting-frameworks" class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Forecasting frameworks</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Driver-based forecasting, pipeline confidence, and scenario planning.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 group-hover:underline">Learn more →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/services/leadership-cadence" class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Leadership cadence</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Weekly rhythm, accountability loops, and leadership team performance.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 group-hover:underline">Learn more →</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Insights -->
    <section class="border-t">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">Insights</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Frameworks and practical notes on scaling execution.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/insights" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 hover:underline">View all insights</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <a href="/insights/execution-discipline/" class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">Featured</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Execution discipline: the missing operating layer</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Scaling fails when strategy outruns operating mechanics. Here’s the minimal layer that makes execution predictable.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 group-hover:underline">Read →</p>
          </a>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-slate-50 p-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Publishing cadence</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Keep this updated with short, structured posts you can share with CEOs and investors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
